msgstr "Gece Nöbetçisi"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:167
#: data/campaigns/Descent_Into_Darkness/scenarios/07_A_Small_Favor.cfg:168
